    Title: Surangama Sutra
    Location: I
Tags:
  - Discernment-Truth=Knowledge=Profane Learning
  - 329
---
When Ananda came into the presence of the Lord Buddha, he bowed down to the
ground in great humility, blaming himself that he had not yet fully developed
the potentialities of Enlightenment, because from the beginning of his previous
lives, he had too much devoted himself to study and learning.
